     <h3><xar:mlstring>Privilege Masks [TODO]</xar:mlstring></h3>

    <p><xar:mlstring>You can set privileges for this module based on the following included masks:</xar:mlstring></p>
        <ul>
            <li><xar:mlstring>ViewLists: allows overview of example items</xar:mlstring></li>
            <li><xar:mlstring>ReadLists: allows reading of fully displayed example items</xar:mlstring></li>
            <li><xar:mlstring>EditLists: permits editing of an example item</xar:mlstring></li>
            <li><xar:mlstring>AddLists: permits addition and editing of an example item</xar:mlstring></li>
            <li><xar:mlstring>DeleteLists: allows deletion, addition and editing of an example item</xar:mlstring></li>
            <li><xar:mlstring>AdminLists: permits access to administrate the Lists module</xar:mlstring></li>

        </ul>
